{"tid":479002,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女追男) 成日去一間文具舖..對個店員有興趣,可以點識","createTime":"2017-11-24T15:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T12:23:45.000Z","uid":65487,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e0112d2d687139ffec06471c2c3ab87f67ffd7ef","tid":479002,"uid":65487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"話說因為工作關係，前幾個月開始，<br />\n我一星期至少會去一次果間文具舖，<br />\n有時一星期三次添<br />\n咁個男店員都認得我既  （目測佢應該 26 27歲左右）<br />\n不過我同佢既交流都只係停留於「又黎喇」「今日咁早既」一句起兩句止既交流<br />\n不過唔知點解我會開始對佢有好感，好突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢又唔係男神型<br />\n<br />\n想集思廣益下點樣可以同佢混熟啲先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.s.唔知佢有冇另一半，又要諗下計點樣探到佢有冇另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596c023acfa74a526791ba0a21542f3b06a9c3fa","tid":479002,"uid":147527,"like":110,"dislike":8,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"可唔可以賣個擦膠比我？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我既心底擦走你"},{"pid":"433a005e44488364107a1d26a4a7704941ba75d5","tid":479002,"uid":65487,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以賣個擦膠比我？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我既心底擦走你</blockquote><br />\n嘩 我驚嚇死佢<br />\n好骨痺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d6431df715ff85db011f0fd12305133dd03a60","tid":479002,"uid":49258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"屌咩，你標題頭幾隻字都答左自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"